In general, the non negative integral solutions of  $x_1+x_2+x_3+....x_k = n$ is given by $\binom{n+k-1}{k-1}$, $\binom{n-1}{k-1}$.
So the number of ways is $\binom{4+4-1}{4-1} =\binom{7}{3}= 35$.
